{"tid":888043,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"和氣食堂 食評","createTime":"2018-11-03T12:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T06:08:54.000Z","uid":175988,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e01912740af577735c47b2855fea5b1742f86906","tid":888043,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:04:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>和氣食堂 @ 黃大仙中心</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CoAOpdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCoAOpdR.jpg&h=80ef85f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>白咖哩鳥冬 + 炸雞</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炸雞唔錯，皮脆肉滑，帶肉汁同油份，調味適中<br />\n鳥冬口感特別，爽滑嘅咖哩鳥冬加上起沙嘅薯蓉泡沫原來幾㚒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咖哩汁辛香而不嗆，濃度啱啱好，食完唔會太膩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改錯名，成碗嘢同白咖哩完全唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n薯蓉泡沫欠缺奶油味，太過稀身，撈埋之後有啲水汪汪咁<br />\n<br />\n結論:食物配搭特別，整體質素中上，一試無妨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236c3ae64b108a4cca769b5de997b311bb014884","tid":888043,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"咖哩係邊"},{"pid":"a8e26dcdc24f3c99e598500924d969893ed70228","tid":888043,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f333bd8592fb1578bf40595c01fd8bd804979b46","tid":888043,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:07:14.000Z","msg":"HOW MUCH 大聲D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f521ac05a68b6f760c9eda25c57e60d115e13f8","tid":888043,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"236c3ae64b108a4cca769b5de997b311bb014884","tid":888043,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cite